’’Ł@7945da62fa463dcc9d3a205e31fadb964f72a38a67d2d0c3df44f72f30033dd6ŚiTitle: Float
Path: Float
Content:
Description:

Numbers with some fractional component
Annotation:

``float``

Literal syntax:

A decimal numeric value including a decimal place. E.g., 
``1.5``
, 
``2.0``
, 
``-15.333``

Casts:

[link: /commands/docs/into_float.md] ``into float``
See also:

[link: /book/types_of_data.md#floatsdecimals] Types of Data - Floats
’Ł@f765a46ddfbbf6414fed02592e5fe5f8f5af920969d34af33fa52f8962d859faŁ‚Title: Float
Path: Additional language notes
Content:
Floats are internally represented as IEEE-754 floats with 64 bit precision.
